---
// About.astro - Static component for the about section
---

<section id="about">
	<h2>About Me</h2>
	<div class="about-content">
		<div class="about-text">
			<p>
				I'm a software developer with strong experience in C++ development, 
				focusing on performance-critical applications and system-level programming.
			</p>
			<p>
				I'm passionate about writing clean, efficient code and continuously learning 
				new technologies. Currently exploring modern web development with Astro and React 
				to broaden my skill set and build full-stack applications.
			</p>
			<p>
				When I'm not coding, you'll find me [add your hobbies/interests here].
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	#about {
		background: white;
	}

	.about-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.about-text p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.about-text p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}
</style>
